      "id": 65,
      "title": "Flat bread",
      "description": "Quick, simple, flat bread made with yogurt so they are very soft. Excellent for dips.",
      "contents": "# Ingredients\r\n\r\n*   200g greek yogurt\n\r\n*   200g plain flour\n\r\n*   5g salt\n\r\n*   1tsp baking powder\n\n\r\n\r\n# Directions\r\n\r\n*   Mix all the ingredients in a food processor or mixer until it forms a ball.\n\r\n*   Leave to rest in a bowl for 30 minutes or so.\n\r\n*   Divide into 4 and roll into thin circles\n\r\n*   Dry fry, one at a time, in a hot frypan for 2-3 minutes each side.\n\r\n*   Wrap in a tea towel until ready to eat.\n\n",
