      "title": "Seafood laksa",
      "description": "Still a work in progress. Quantities are for 2 people.",
      "contents": "# Ingredients\r\n\r\n## Seafood\r\n\r\n*   2 small red mullet\n\r\n*   10 raw prawns\n\r\n*   2 medium sized squid\n\n\r\n\r\n## Paste\r\n\r\n*   2 shallots\n\r\n*   2 small, hot, green chillies\n\r\n*   Ginger\n\r\n*   Galangal\n\r\n*   1-2 tbsp shrimp paste\n\r\n*   Half a tsp of tumeric\n\n\r\n\r\n Other ingredients\r\n\r\n*   A bunch of corriander\n\r\n*   Something green, e.g. green beens, baby pak choix.\n\r\n*   Bean sproutes or noodles (or both)\n\n\n",
